# Quartz site builder
# site/.gitignore is not tracked (Quartz ignores it), so list the exclusions here too.
# node_modules/ is also excluded from iCloud sync by adding it here, but note that
# iCloud for Windows has no .nosync equivalent — if sync bandwidth is a concern,
# consider moving the site/ folder outside iCloud Drive after cloning.
site/node_modules/
site/public/
site/.quartz-cache/
site/.quartz/